race.comment: VICTORIA FEVER (11) was below her best last time, finishing sixth and beaten 13 lengths over 1300m at Maronas. Finds the right race this time and can bounce back. LEOPARDISIMA (1) is usually thereabouts but finds it hard to win, with only one victory from 10 starts. Did a good job last start to finish third over 1300m at this track, beaten 6 lengths. Hard to beat in this suitable race. SUDAMERICANA (2) finished out of the money two starts back then was beaten 6 lengths when fifth in a 1400m contest at this track five weeks ago. Finds a nice race and can figure in the finish. AKASHI (6) finished 11 lengths away in sixth at her last appearance over 1400m at Maronas on October 26. Solid top-three chance on her best figures.
